title: Hour 3 - Bill Russell the Man, Jerry West
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Bill Russell the Man, Jerry West
description:
Dan talks about the late Bill Russell in terms of his contributions as a man more than just a player and coach. And Russell's longtime rival, friend and fellow Hall of Fame player, Jerry West stops by to talk about the kind of man he was.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
